Class ExecutedExam

  • java.lang.Object
    • models.ExecutedExam
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class ExecutedExam
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Class that represent all the information after executed an exam (happens after the teacher freeze - close the exam or at the end of time given).
